{"tid":1849470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線！大埔有人疑似賣二手口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T05:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:17:54.000Z","uid":329170,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d50e3d641c46e8f60506356893ec7fc5f4e85f1","tid":1849470,"uid":329170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"今日中午行經過大埔富善街，見到個男人係相中右面白色箱度拎一包包口罩出黎賣，一開始啲人經過都係望下，冇人行埋去買。<br />\n<br />\n之後個男人大聲叫賣：$80一包，50個<br />\n<br />\n啲廢老就陸續行埋去，而我覺得佢好可疑，所以行埋去睇。我見到佢包裝只係普通透明包裝袋，入面啲口罩條帶又黃黃地，口罩表面都唔係出面正貨嘅咁乾淨，咁我就問佢：邊度出產架？佢就有啲心虛咁話：緊係香港啦。<br />\n<br />\n隔離啲師奶就大大聲話：而家抗疫呀，話知佢邊度出產都要買架啦。之後個師奶好似買左🤦🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n個男人見我咁問，佢就補充話：放心啦，乾淨架。咁我望多兩望就走，佢離遠大大聲咁話我：咁你去藥房買啲日本產嘅口罩囉。<br />\n<br />\n個男人存貨唔多，但已經有幾個人買左🤦🏻&zwj;♀️🤦🏻&zwj;♀️🤦🏻&zwj;♀️如果社區爆發就係呢啲黑心人傳開去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2noxzv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2noxzv.png&h=e5a34c27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1edc27cf04133b00dae4e14de4585756ec0d3453","tid":1849470,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3326764ed6942df227289aeb8361c22ed6671428","tid":1849470,"uid":271413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"咁既包裝都有人買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b4909fd37b9137682ef3e1f95ecc526dd7cdbe","tid":1849470,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Ji2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=252b0268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/p